quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  36,28,"Men hatonjinaano e halkirgol yim…ďe makko fennunoo…ďe …ďen wari mo, e koneeli Malaa'ika, …ói Men jippinirta ka kammu. Tawde fii ma…ď…ďe no hoyani Men diini …óum. Ko Men e…ď…ďirnoo halakuyee ma…ď…ďe on, ko haacaango immorde ka kammu, wanaa jippingol Malaa'ika ko lepte …ďe."
  36,29,"Halkeede yim…ďe makko …ďen wonaano, si wanaa haacaango wooto, ngo Men wuurti e ma…ď…ďe, tawi …ďe tallii hay gooto heddaaki, fii ma…ď…ďe gasii. No …ďe wa…ótiniri non, ko wano yiite hu…ď…ďunoonge, nge √Īifi, hara ba…óte magge heddaaki."
  36,30,"Ee ninse jeyaa…ďe fennunoo…ďe, ee hayrere ma…ď…ďe √Ďalnde Darngal, tuma …ďe yi'oyta lepte …óen! Ko tawde …ďe woniino ka aduna ma…ď…ďe, Nulaa…óo kala arunoo…óo …ďe immorde ka Alla, …ďe wa…ótayno mo jalnori, …ďe jalkita mo. Ba…ótane ma…ď…ďe …óen wonti ninse √Ďalnde Darngal, fii ko …ďe fantini kon e bannge Alla."
  36,31,"E …ďee fennoo…ďe jalkita Nulaa…ďe yi'aali …ďe waajitora mofte adinoo…ďe …ďe? ∆Āe annda …ďen …óon maayiino, …ďe artataa aduna han kadi. ∆Āe yahdii e kuu…óe ma…ď…ďe. Wonnde Alla yo…ďitoyay …ďe …óum."
  36,32,"Mofte …óen fow wonaali, si wanaa moo…ďoytee…ďe ka Amen √Ďalnde Darngal, tuma …ďe immintinaa, fii yo…ďitugol …ďe golle ma…ď…ďe."
  36,33,"Hujja ummital ngal no woodani fennu…ďe …ďen: e leydi yoorundi hokki ndin, Men jippini to…ďo e mayri, immorde ka kammu, Men fu…óini e mayri nooneeji pu…ói, Men yaltini nooneeji e gabbe, e nder …óin pu…ói, fii ko yim…ďe …ďen √Īaama. Yo …ďe anndu non, wuurnir…óo ndin leydi …óon non, ko hattan…óo wuurnitugol maay…ďe."
  36,34,"Men wa…ói e ndin leydi ndi Men jippini to…ďo e mun, gese le…ó…óe tamarooje e inabuuje. Men …ďulliti ton …ďulli ndiyam, ko …óe yarniree."
  36,35,"Men wa…óiri …óen gese, fii no yim…ďe …ďen √Īaamira e majje, immorde e kon ko Alla neemini e ma…ď…ďe, hara …ďe yannganaaki …óum. E …ďee yettirtaa Alla e …óii neemaaji …óon, rewugol Mo Kanko tun, gom…óina kadi Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen?"
  36,36,"Senaade woodanii Alla, O toowii. On fu…ó…óu…óo nooneeji …óin fow: gila e pu…ói e le…ó…óe, haa e wonkiiji yim…ďe …ďen, tawde O wa…óirii …ďe deyel e gorel, e kon ko …ďe anndaa fii mun, e tagu Alla ngun ka njorndi e maayo ekn."
  36,37,"Hujja goo wonanii yim…ďe …ďen e fii wootin…óingol Alla, tawde Me…óen na…ďira ndaygu ngun, na…ďugol √Īalorma on, adda jemma on, tuma Men sortata √Īalorma on e makko, Men wa…óta …óum niwre, haa yim…ďe …ďen naatii e mayre."
  36,38,"Maande goo hollaynde …ďe gootaagu Alla ngun, ko ngee naange dogaynge haa e √Īii…ďirde nge Alla anndi e…ď…ďoore mun, nge ha…óta …óon. Nden, ko e…ď…ďoore Foolu…óo Mo fooletaake On, Anndu…óo Mo huunde e fiyakuuji tagu Makko ngun wirnanaaki Mo."
  36,39,"Maande goo kadi tinndinnde e gootaagu Alla senii…óo On, ko nduu lewru, ndu Men e…ď…ďani jipporde jemma kala. Ndu fu…ó…óora toksuru, hooti ndu mawna, hooti ndu fan…óita, haa ndu wa…ótinira wano baaŇčal tamarohi e noone mun ka soy…óugol e ka hi…ó…óugol."
  36,40,"Maandeeji naange ngen e lewru ndun, e jamma on e √Īalorma on, ko Alla elti …ói. ∆äi ha…ótanaa yawtugol ko …ói e…ď…ďanaa kon. Wanaa naange ngen woni ko waawi hewtitorgol lewru ndun, waylugol dogudu magge maa na…ďugol ndaygu magge, wanaa jemaa on kadi ha…ótanaa aditagol √Īalorma on, ado o lannude. ∆äi fow majji non, e kala koode e ruugay…ói, ko eltanaa…ói laawi heerii…ói."